%F A104887 T(n,k) = A000040(n-k+1); a(n) = A000040(A004736(n)).
%F A104887 a(n) = A000040(m), where m=(t*t+3*t+4)/2-n, t=floor((-1+sqrt(8*n-7))/2). - _Boris Putievskiy_, Dec 13 2012
